{"tid":2322500,"cid":5,"subCid":11,"title":"游梁成魔六步曲","createTime":"2020-12-12T11:09:53.000Z","updateTime":"2020-12-12T23:58:55.000Z","uid":230530,"like":2,"dislike":53,"uniUserReply":9,"replies":[{"pid":"393006c28eb2e8657c23bd9165d88d74e2c86202","tid":2322500,"uid":230530,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-12-12T11:09:53.000Z","msg":"女偏激 男投機 同上「邪路」<br />\n<br />\n「青症雙邪」游蕙禎和梁頌恆在立法會宣誓中「玩」，最後被取消資格，也淪為香港主流社會的公敵。不少市民都會質疑：「為何好端端的兩個年輕人，會有辱國辱華的心態，會走去煽動『港獨』？」本報總結二人成長、求學、參與所謂「社會運動」、參選區議會及立法會，重組他們的「成魔六步曲」：2003年的反廿三條立法的遊行、2012年的反國教集會、2014年的「佔領」行動，都對兩人影響極深，更造就兩人無視法治甚至否定「一國兩制」的<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/nJ7JK6e.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FnJ7JK6e.jpg&h=6206eccc&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n偏激與投機性格。"},{"pid":"a91123af2623d7e5e607d5adf6f3940e89755257","tid":2322500,"uid":33618,"like":0,"dislike":3,"score":-3,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-12-12T11:13:04.000Z","msg":"飛輪海頭<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/haha.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"be7890f987336f13facfa35b897f9efa5039dcfa","tid":2322500,"uid":54876,"like":0,"dislike":5,"score":-5,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-12-12T11:18:20.000Z","msg":"作為一個學生妹，係幾柒下"},{"pid":"4fd5bc8a35685559ce41c28088293466807b5494","tid":2322500,"uid":212168,"like":0,"dislike":2,"score":-2,"quote":{"pid":"be7890f987336f13facfa35b897f9efa5039dcfa","tid":2322500,"uid":54876,"like":0,"dislike":5,"score":-5,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-12-12T11:18:20.000Z","msg":"作為一個學生妹，係幾柒下"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-12-12T12:17:47.000Z","msg":"想同bb瘋狂爆房"},{"pid":"17e4955a70d2c1deb628998dad3ab48607bbab26","tid":2322500,"uid":143016,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-12-12T12:20:24.000Z","msg":"你出post 都幾密 btw 你老母死未？"},{"pid":"08006ed28aaae8585616936b8dd17e2659647d66","tid":2322500,"uid":71620,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-12-12T12:44:02.000Z","msg":"佢地有無卜過野<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/wonder.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"07d867419e8